imagery in your book

00:30:10.910 --> 00:30:14.675 align:middle line:84%
of those elementals
that go along with fire.

00:30:14.675 --> 00:30:15.300 align:middle line:90%
>>COOPER: Yeah.

00:30:15.300 --> 00:30:19.460 align:middle line:84%
