part of the fire fairy realm

00:30:29.650 --> 00:30:31.140 align:middle line:90%
at one point.

00:30:31.140 --> 00:30:35.750 align:middle line:84%
Interestingly enough,
when we call in fire,

00:30:35.750 --> 00:30:40.880 align:middle line:84%
we cannot get fire without
a salamander or a Shallore.

00:30:40.880 --> 00:30:42.310 align:middle line:90%
They come into being.

00:30:42.310 --> 00:30:46.120 align:middle line:84%
They spark the flame
when we light a match.

00:30:46.120 --> 00:30:51.070 align:middle line:84%
