physicality into ether,

00:31:11.250 --> 00:31:11.970 align:middle line:90%
so to speak.

00:31:11.970 --> 00:31:13.400 align:middle line:90%
And into ash.

00:31:13.400 --> 00:31:16.800 align:middle line:84%
So they're responsible for
the recycling of matter

00:31:16.800 --> 00:31:18.270 align:middle line:90%
on our planet.

00:31:18.270 --> 00:31:21.580 align:middle line:84%
And without them, we
wouldn't have heat.

00:31:21.580 --> 00:31:23.420 align:middle line:90%
We wouldn't have food.

00:31:23.420 --> 00:31:25.060 align:middle line:90%
We wouldn't have anything.

00:31:25.060 --> 00:31:28.610 align:middle line:84%
So obviously, they are
aligned to the sunlight,

00:31:28.610 --> 00:31:29.790 align:middle line:90%
which makes sense.

00:31:29.790 --> 00:31:31.060 align:middle line:90%
They all are.

00:31:31.060 --> 00:31:31.640 align:middle line:90%
But yeah.

00:31:31.640 --> 00:31:35.240 align:middle line:84%
So every time you light a
match to build your fire,

00:31:35.240 --> 00:31:38.732 align:middle line:84%
thank a salamander
or a Shallore.

00:31:38.732 --> 00:31:40.440 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And then
start, maybe, watching

00:31:40.440 --> 00:31:44.325 align:middle line:84%
for the faces and the images
